A new helper function xe_bo_has_single_placement() to check
if a BO has single placement.

Reviewed-by: Jos√© Roberto de Souza <jose.souza@intel.com>
Acked-by: Lionel Landwerlin <lionel.g.landwerlin@intel.com>
